{
  "stem": "16345.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyhow, we ate it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we almost died, because evidently, we didn't know what pickled oysters were supposed to taste like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But those things were bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after that, it took me 30 years before I touched another oyster.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyhow, we ate those oysters with relish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "While one was guarding the other back, the other one ate the oysters, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They had a huge pit on one side of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And every day, they grabbed a bunch of prisoners-- and a lot of people were dying-- to, to take all the corpses and throw them in the pit.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one day when I was taken to work the corpses and throw them in the pit, I noticed that a lot of the corpses in the pit had pieces of their buttocks missing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's when I realized that the roasting that was going on wasn't all rats and cats.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was some of that going on also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I tried, I tried to stay away from trading for some of the pieces of roast.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I wasn't into that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Also we got-- we ran into some good luck in that camp, my buddy and I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "About 300 or 400 yards away, there was a train parked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the train had food on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It had vegetables.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, you could see those large cabbages, and kohlrabi that which the Germans absolutely loved, and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day, one night, we decided we were going to rob the train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we didn't see any guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They felt so safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we went and tied our pants and our jackets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we loaded up with potatoes and all those goodies.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
